  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether injection needle pen point type 'PP Gauge
      25' should be recommended as a primary choice of needle (in stead of 'PP Gauge 27') for
      healthy pregnant women who at delivery (vaginal or cesarean section) get spinal anesthesia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
